metadata.name: Lake of Serenity #K23001
metadata.description:
Beautiful and calming lake surrounded with the heights of mountain peaks and trees.

The lake seemed to stretched  forever as if the mountain was slowly drowning and create a perfect mirror of itself.

The lake can truly be an inspirational place where imagination live where the magical things happen where your soul is soothed by it's serene.

Whatever brings you to the lake take a breath and enjoy the stillness.

Created by Kumoto Sakti from June 21  - July 8, 2022 / Ai Generated Artwork / 5120x3072px
